{
  "title": "Refactoring Machine Learning Training Loops using FastAPI in Python 3.12+",
  "summary": "This explainer demonstrates the process of refactoring traditional machine learning (ML) training loops to be more modular, scalable, and API-friendly using FastAPI and Python 3.12+. It provides code examples and notes on version updates and potential caveats.",
